snippet.title: Hot Shots Tennis - Gameplay Video 1 | PS2 on PS4
snippet.description:
Gameplay footage from the Hot Shots Tennis PS2™ game on the PS4™ system. Experience Hot Shots Tennis with 1080p up-rendering and Trophies. Additional enhanced features include Share Play (Active PS Plus membership may be required), Remote Play, Activity Feeds and Second Screen support for game manuals through the PS Vita system or PlayStation App.

© 2007 Sony Interactive Entertainment Inc.
